<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THE LOVE OF COUPLE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chung Pathien vabang pil lungsieta dim,
 Na lungsietna chawnban zaitha hatin puiin;
 Lungkhat a luongin hinkhuo guibang sau hen,
 Thimthu tiem pello a, kilungsiet zing di'n.

[V2]
 Kilungsietna manglo di'n,
 Damlai sunni tum ma'n;
 Gimtheia al-ang vai lo di'n,
 Nangin khawtuoh zingin.

[V3]
 2. Sietlei lungkhamna, buoina lakah le,
 Lalpa, Na khut hat in puiin, lumbang sungin;
 Damlai sunni tum macheng Na na sema,
 Sawlbang heina chenga Na min zah zel di'n.

[V4]
 3. Phung bang vukin Lalpa amau nih hi,
 Kipah bukimna'n vawn zatam paibang kuoh di'n;
 A chung u-ah Na vangphatna ni vak hen!
 Changbang dam kumkhuo sawta kizahtuoh di'n.</lyrics>
<author>T. Dolien</author>
<hymn_number>441</hymn_number>
</song>